label: AB5_oP24_62_c_3cd-001
title: SrZn$_{5}$ Structure
comments:
(Baenziger, 1956) give this structure in the $Pmcn$ setting of space group \#62.  We used FINDSYM to place it in the standard $Pnma$ setting. 
 At high temperatures SrZn$_{5}$ transforms into the  \href{current_web_home_dir/AB5_hP6_191_a_cg-001}{CaCu$_{5}$ ($D2_{d}$) structure}. (Wendorff, 2007) 
 This is the binary form of the \href{current_web_home_dir/A2B3C_oP24_62_d_3c_c-001}{SrAu$_{3}$Al$_{2}$ structure}.
